# Review Execution

## Workflow contract
The GitHub workflow must match the real script CLI signatures exactly.

## Local execution
- `make test`
- `make review-local BASE_REF=HEAD~1 HEAD_REF=HEAD`
- `make validate-policy`

## If changing script arguments
You must update:
- workflow YAML
- Makefile
- README.md
- CLAUDE.md
- TESTING.md
